docs/v3-to-v4-migration-guide.md
     1вҶ’# TS-Pattern v3 to v4 Migration Guide
     3вҶ’## Breaking changes
     5вҶ’### Imports
     7вҶ’type-specific wildcard patterns have moved from `__.<pattern>` to a new `Pattern` qualified module, also exported as `P` by ts-pattern.
     8вҶ’
     9вҶ’```diff
    10вҶ’- import { match, __ } from 'ts-pattern';
    11вҶ’+ import { match, Pattern } from 'ts-pattern';
    12вҶ’
    13вҶ’
    14вҶ’const toString = (value: string | number) =>
    15вҶ’  match(value)
    16вҶ’-   .with(__.string, (v) => v)
    17вҶ’-   .with(__.number, (v) => `${v}`)
    18вҶ’+   .with(Pattern.string, (v) => v)
    19вҶ’+   .with(Pattern.number, (v) => `${v}`)
    20вҶ’    .exhaustive();
    21вҶ’```
    22вҶ’
    23вҶ’or
    24вҶ’
    25вҶ’```diff
      вҶ’вҖҰ
    39вҶ’#### `__` вҖҰ
    57вҶ’#### `select()`, `not()`, `when()` вҖҰ
    79вҶ’#### `Pattern` type вҖҰ
   122вҶ’## New features вҖҰ
   128вҶ’#### `P.array(pattern)` вҖҰ
   159вҶ’#### `P.optional(pattern)` вҖҰ
   201вҶ’#### `P.union(...patterns)` вҖҰ
   234вҶ’#### `P.intersection(...patterns)` вҖҰ
   298вҶ’#### `P.infer<typeof pattern>` вҖҰ
   336вҶ’#### `P.symbol` вҖҰ
   346вҶ’#### `P.bigint` вҖҰ
