     1вҶ’# TS-Pattern v4 to v5 Migration Guide
     3вҶ’This file contains all breaking changes and new features between the version 4 and 5 of TS-Pattern.
     4вҶ’
     5вҶ’# Breaking changes
     7вҶ’## TypeScript v5
     9вҶ’Because it relies on [const type parameters](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/release-notes/typescript-5-0.html#const-type-parameters), TS-Pattern v5 requires TypeScript v5+!
    10вҶ’
    11вҶ’## `.with` is now evaluated eagerly вҖҰ
    42вҶ’## Matching on Map and Sets вҖҰ
    63вҶ’# New features
    65вҶ’## chainable methods
    67вҶ’TS-Pattern v5's major addition is the ability to chain methods to narrow down the values matched by primitive patterns, like `P.string` or `P.number`.
    68вҶ’
    69вҶ’Since a few examples is worth a thousand words, here are a few ways you can use chainable methods:
    70вҶ’
